* Don't let the Premature Optimization Pattern prevent you from Designing For Performance.  Every web project risks being viewed as non-performant during testing if certain optimization steps are not taken early on.  Risks are non-productive interference from outside "experts" and cycles spent re-assuring stake-holders.\
\
