       Starting with "index.html".\
       SEO support, how images can impact performance.\
       Repaints/reflows can be costly and $digest cycles can have a huge impact.\
       How using ng-class instead of ng-show/ng-hide can help.       \
2) Size matters\
       Strategies for minimizing application size/weight.\
       Proxy Pattern (Lazy Instantiation Pattern)\
       How grunt can help.\
3) Connections:\
       Strategies for minimizing connections.\
       Perceived vs Actual performance and how lazy loading can have an impact.\
4) Minimize the impact of $digest cycles:\
       How using $scope state in lieu of function/method calls in partials helps.\
       Smart loading of partials, minimize total number loading for a given view/state.\
